author: Dana Velden
title: 13 Fast and Fresh Chicken Dinners — Recipes from The Kitchn
text:
Share 
A bevy of quick chicken dinners is a fantastic thing to have in your recipe repertoire. I mean, who hasn't come home from a long day, tired, hungry, and in need of something delicious and quick to get on the table? Chicken will save you, every time. Here are 13 examples of how beautifully that's going to work for you.
